data.text:
TVGN Counts Down Sequels That Were Better Than the Original

It's rare that a movie sequel matches the quality of the original, and even more rare when it surpasses the first. So what's the greatest movie sequel of all time? TVGN counts down 25 Sequels Better Than the Original Monday at 9/8c. Which ones do you hope make the list? Weigh in below — and check out a clip of the countdown below:

Francis Ford Coppola Receives Oscar Lifetime Achievement Award

Francis Ford Coppola received the Irving G. Thalberg award from the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Science's over the weekend during an Oscar ceremony in Los Angeles.  "I've learned how to spend money, and Francis has learned how to make it," producer George Lucas said during his tribute to Coppola.
